entries.femaleVariant: There's no such thing as Agwe! It's all made-up.
But there was another Agwe, the real one. He was called Philippe Oreste.
When the hurricanes hit Haiti, he put everyone on life rafts.
And then they all came to Pacifica.
Ever seen a map? You know where Haiti is and Pacifica is?
Then... then they just got to land, first.
And they drove all the way to Pacifica.
There were two Agwes. One was a loa, but loas aren't actually real.
